data.description: Come Home to this brick 3 bedroom 2.5 bath home. Enjoy the view of the lake while relaxing in your pool. Entering the front door you will notice the hardwood floors through out and the staircase to the second floor. Formal dining on the left with floor to ceiling windows for natural light. The primary bedroom is on the first floor. Large ensuite bathroom with walk in shower and separate garden tub. Large walk in closet. The great room is on the back with views of the lake and pool. Wood burning fireplace and built in book case. This room is great for entertaining because of the size and the flow of the house. The kitchen is loaded with cabinets and also a built in bakers cabinet. Large and open it centers around an island with a beautiful wood countertop. All stainless appliances stay. Just off the kitchen is a large pantry with wood shelving. A nice half bath is just off the back foyer coming in from the back screened porch. Oversized laundry room with a big closet large enough for freezer. Up stairs there are 3 more spacious bedrooms all with walk in closets. There is a wonderful storage area with all wood shelves. Outside you will find the cutest cottage. It offers living area with high ceilings, bedroom, sunroom and a kitchen with refrigerator and sink. There is also a storage building for all your outdoor things. Large yard with circular drive. If you enjoy swimming, fishing or kayaking you will love this property. Call an agent to view today.
